body_html:
Oh thank you @momeara for filling the issue.
I just wanted to do it by myself.
We have the same problem in our home-compiled TF since the 1.9.rc0 or rc1.
BTW I think the commit introduced it is 80fc661#diff-06268ec57b0c7871d7e7cab011778559
and there is a related issue that was closed with no resolution #19840

body:
Oh thank you @momeara for filling the issue. 
I just wanted to do it by myself. 
We have the same problem in our  home-compiled TF since the 1.9.rc0 or rc1.
BTW I think the commit introduced it is https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/commit/80fc661853f9a0844faf95eb68438dc85a5879e3#diff-06268ec57b0c7871d7e7cab011778559
and there is a related issue that was closed with no resolution https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/issues/19840
